1510
01:18:14,770 --> 01:18:16,550
Ever since Jesse told me he couldn't sleep

1511
01:18:16,550 --> 01:18:17,383
'cause he was staying up-
- Hey, Burt, Burt.

1512
01:18:17,383 --> 01:18:18,216
- All night reading your letters.

